# Unified vecinita-llm Modal app (ADR-037)

Vecinita has **one** Modal LLM deployable: **`vecinita-llm`** (`infra/modal/llm_app.py`).

## Do

- Route **all** LLM HTTP (chat, eval, ingest/retag, playground list/pull) through
  `VECINITA_MODAL_LLM_URL` + optional `VECINITA_MODAL_PROXY_KEY`.
- Use **vLLM** for inference; **HuggingFace Hub** (`huggingface_hub.snapshot_download`) for
  `pull_model_job` / `stage_default_model` — not `ollama pull`.
- Keep API path compat: `GET/POST /models/ollama` on `vecinita-llm` (Ollama-style tags in UI;
  tag→HF mapping in `infra/modal/llm_model_registry.py`).
- Store weights on Modal volume **`llm-models`** only; manifest at `/models/manifest.json`.
- Accept optional `model_id` on `/generate`, `/warm` (playground tags).

## Do not

- Deploy or add routes to **`vecinita-ollama`** — deprecated; de-deploy after unified smoke.
- Add `VECINITA_MODAL_OLLAMA_URL` to new DO specs or sync lists (legacy env may warn-only in clients).
- Assume vLLM can read Ollama blob cache — incompatible formats.

## Model switching

One vLLM engine per GPU class instance; changing `model_id` reloads the engine (~60–120s).
Use `/warm` before eval batches.

